@deciek Have not seen the sketches - would love to! The ethnicity is difficult to determine, Castledermot was in the periphery zone influenced by Dublin in the 10th c, but the area was mostly inhabited by Irish people. There is a recorded Viking raid in Castledermot in the early 9th c.
